ls -mtp
`m` : separate by commas
`t` : sort by time modified
`p` : write a slash `/` after each directory 

Steps: 
-----
- To create the file: 
vim midLS
i #to open insert mode
ls -mtp
esc:wq #to write and quit which means save and close
